  "title": "Project manager",
  "description": "<ul><li>Assist\n     the Project Director in day-to-day site operations and coordination of\n     construction activities.</li><li>Monitor\n     project progress, prepare reports, and ensure work is completed according\n     to schedule and quality standards.</li><li>Liaise\n     with clients, subcontractors, suppliers, and relevant authorities to\n     facilitate smooth project execution.</li><li>Supervise\n     site workers, enforce safety regulations, and resolve on-site issues\n     promptly.</li><li>Support\n     in preparing project documentation, including work schedules, progress\n     claims, and site inspection records.</li><li>Ensure\n     compliance with Singapore’s construction regulations and company policies.</li><li>Perform\n     any other related duties as assigned by the management.</li></ul>",
